body.description: Transform the look of your home with the Superior Afton Acid Wash Modern Gradient Indoor Area Rug or Runner. This eclectic and vintage-inspired rug is expertly crafted from Polypropylene and a sturdy jute backing. Featuring a 0.39" pile height, this unique rug is an excellent, long-lasting and practical option for your tile or hardwood floors. This ultra-soft and durable material can withstand high traffic rooms, perfect for homes with children and pets. The durable material, abstract ombre gradient pattern, and practical design is what makes this rug a one-of-a-kind centerpiece for your home.

productInformation.name: Product Care Instructions
productInformation.value: Vacuum regularly to prevent dust and crumbs from setting into the fibers. Avoid continuous exposure to sunlight. Use scissors to remove any loose ends. Turn from time to time to equalize wear. Spot clean for best results

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why Superior? We created superior products to fill your life with long-lasting luxury. Our company has grown into an affordable home luxury brand specializing in area rugs and bedding specializing in area rugs, bedding, bath linens, and curtains. All products are made with premium materials that have been designed to bring you a consistently exceptional experience SUPERIOR AFTON MODERN GRADIENT INDOOR AREA RUG Bring a texture-rich feel to your interiors with this ombre area rug The Afton Acid Wash Area Rug from Superior has a unique design that will complement any room in your home. The popular distressed, abstract pattern creates a dramatic pop of color by using deep, rich, vibrant tones that attract attention in your favorite space. FEATURES: 0.39” rug thickness is easy to maintain, allows chairs sitting atop this rug to slide easily, and is sure to clear any doorway in your home. Sturdy power-loomed construction OEKO-TEX certified

COMFORT AND STYLE FIND HARMONY This expressive rug displays a gradient, ombre accent that transitions from one color hue to another to compliment any contemporary living space. HARDWORKING AND VERSATILE Crafted from Polypropylene with a long-lasting jute backing, this family-friendly rug is durable enough to handle your most frequented indoor areas of your home. STYLISH AND PRACTICAL The sturdy power-loomed construction is made with everyday durability to handle your most frequented indoor areas such as kitchens, family rooms, basements, and entryways. COMPLETE THE LOOK OF ANY ROOM Ideal for homes with children and pets, this rug can resist common spills and stains, making it perfect for everyday use.

How to Choose the Right Size Area Rug Runner Rug Size: 2'7"x 8' Recommended Room: Hallway, Entryway, Bedroom Pro tip: Runners are the perfect way to dress up any hallway in your home or decorate any narrow space that could use a cozier foundation. Small Scatter Rugs Size: 2'x3' Recommended Room: Entryway, Kitchen, Bathroom, Laundry Room, Playroom Pro tip: This versatile rectangular size works great in front of doorways and can also work as a small landing space when you need a little extra padding. Medium-Size Rugs: 4'x6', 5'x8' Recommended Room: Living Room, Bedroom, Playroom, Dining Room Pro tip: Perfect for smaller living spaces, it's easy to define a specific seating area with a medium-size rug. Large-Size Area Rugs: 8'x10' Recommended Room: Bedroom, Living Room, Dining Rooms, Nursery Pro tip: Create a central focus to any medium or large living area that provides a soft cushion underfoot while also framing your space.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars COMPLETELY DIFFERENT COLOR
reviews.reviewText: First let me say, the rug is very nice, durable, and definitely worth the money. However, the color is completely different than the shown picture. In the picture, the color looks tan and reddish, but in person, the color is a dark burgundy and grey. Here comes the crazy part. When I took the picture of the rug to show to my boyfriend, on the picture that I took, the color of the rug looks tan and reddish. The rug is in my laundry room, so it's fine with my decor in there. However, if it had been for a different room, I would have returned it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 16, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this runner!
reviews.reviewText: Gorgeous well priced runner! I love the look as it's an unusual, unique and subtle design. The colors in the picture are accurate too. It's also easy to clean, and hides dirt (I have it in front of the entry) . I liked this so much that I bought 2 more in the other color for my hallways. It's a great value for what you get. You do need to get a rug pad to hold it in place so I bought the Gorilla Grip rug pad and it works perfectly.
